data("anscombe")

an2 <- anscombe %>% 
  gather(key = "key", value="value") %>% 
  separate(key,into = c("var","dataset"),1) %>%
  group_by(dataset, var) %>% 
  mutate(id = row_number()) %>% 
  spread(var, value) %>% 
  select(-id) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  mutate(dataset = paste("Dataset", dataset))
